OL,3,CMan, 28, found guilty of rioting in
OL,4,CEly following the death of two
OL,5,Cteenagers
OL,7,FA man has been found guilty for
OL,8,Fplaying his part in the Ely riots in
OL,9,F2023 after he encouraged others to
OL,10,Fbecome involved in the violence.
OL,12,FAshdon O'Dare, 28, of Penygarn Road,
OL,13,FEly, was found guilty of rioting by a
OL,14,Fjury following a trial at Newport
OL,15,FCrown Court.
OL,17,FThe riot broke out following the
OL,18,Fdeaths of teenagers Kyrees Sullivan,
OL,19,F16, and Harvey Evans, 15, who died as
OL,20,Fa result of an electric bike crash.
