OL,7,FHours of violence and vandalism
OL,8,Ffollowed, with around 150 people
OL,9,Fattending a riot which saw missiles
OL,10,Fthrown at police.
OL,12,FOpening the case to the jury,
OL,13,Fprosecutor Matthew Cobbe said: "Kyrees
OL,14,FSullivan, 16, and Harvey Evans, 15,
OL,15,Fdied on May 22, 2023. They had been
OL,16,Friding an electric bike through Ely.
