OL,3,CMan, 28, found guilty of rioting in
OL,4,CEly following the death of two
OL,5,Cteenagers
OL,7,F"They lost control of the bike as they
OL,8,Fdrove along Snowden Road and crashed.
OL,9,FBoth suffered catastrophic injuries
OL,10,Fbecause of that crash and they died at
OL,11,Fthe scene.
OL,13,F"The emergency services were quick to
OL,14,Farrive. The terrible news travelled
OL,15,Fquickly and large crowds gathered. It
OL,16,Fbecame necessary to set up cordons to
OL,17,Fsecure the area. Footage gathered of
OL,18,Fthe events that followed shows the
OL,19,Finitial grief and distress and anger
OL,20,Fwithin the crowd.
