OL,5,Cteenagers
OL,7,F"Rumours circulated as to the cause of
OL,8,Fthe crash and it was clear from
OL,9,Fcomments being directed and made at
OL,10,Fthe police from the crowd, parts of
OL,11,Fthe crowd believed that the police
OL,12,Fwere being blamed.
OL,14,F"As the minutes wore on a large
OL,15,Fportion of the crowd became hostile,
OL,16,Fdirecting that hostility towards the
OL,17,Fpolice. The hostility escalated
OL,18,Frapidly, it wasn't long before the
OL,19,Fpolice were confronted by a riot."
