OL,5,Cteenagers
OL,7,FDescribing the involvement of O'Dare,
OL,8,Fthe prosecutor said the defendant was
OL,9,Fearly to arrive at the scene and
OL,10,Fbecame "aggressively vocal and
OL,11,Fconfrontational".
OL,13,FThe court heard how O'Dare was
OL,14,Fencouraging those around him to get
OL,15,Finvolved and was accused of "whipping
OL,16,Fup the crowd".
