OL,7,FMr Cobbe said: "He was one of the most
OL,8,Fprominent during the early stages, he
OL,9,Fwas deliberately trying to get a
OL,10,Freaction from others around him. He
OL,11,Fleft early, but only after the bottles
OL,12,Fhad started to be thrown, the riot had
OL,13,Fstarted.
