OL,7,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke, the
OL,8,Frecorder of Cardiff, remanded O'Dare
OL,9,Fon conditional bail until his
OL,10,Fsentencing date on June 8. The
OL,11,Fdefendant will be sentenced alongside
OL,12,F39 other individuals, with the
OL,13,Fsentencing hearing estimated to last
OL,14,Ftwo weeks.
